{
  "doc_id": "24018",
  "text": "A 4-component PFV vector system, consisting of the expression-optimized packaging constructs pcoPG4 (PFV Gag), pcoPE (PFV Env), pcoPP (Pol) or its authentic ORF containing variant pcziPol (PFV Pol), and the enhanced green fluorescent protein (eGFP)-expressing PFV transfer vectors pMD9 or puc2MD9 ( Figure 1B ), has been described previously [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . In some experiments previously described variants of the PFV Pol packaging construct, containing expression-optimized (pcoPP2) or authentic (pcziPol iRT) ORFs with catalytically inactive reverse transcriptase (Pol iRT, YVDD 312-315 GAAA mutation), were used [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] .",
